Package Utilities

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BackgroundEvent_Interface
    Represents an event in the background which would need to be polled for and responded to.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppTester
    Use this for various testing/debugging purposes including multi-threaded print statements with built in stack trace, assertions that stop the entire application rather than just the current thread, and application termination with a full stack trace for terminal error conditions.
    ByteArrays
    Contains array and byte array utilities for things like serialization, deep equals, concatenation, and conversion to hexadeximal format.
    FileFinder
    This class helps find files in the file system on both Linux and Windows.
    Networking_Utilities  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AppTester.DefaultPrintStream
    Used to specify which standard output terminal bound strings should be sent through.
    AppTester.Rank
    Used to rank terminal readouts based on relative importance.
    AppTester.ReadoutCondition
    Used to specify whether something is being printed under an error situation or a non-error situation.
